---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="About — Aryan D Haritsa">

  <!-- Header -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-grid bg-grid-fade opacity-40 pointer-events-none"></div>
    <div class="container-wide pt-20 pb-14 relative">
      <p class="eyebrow reveal mb-5">Background · Interests · Where I'm going</p>
      <h1 class="reveal text-5xl md:text-7xl font-light tracking-[-0.035em] leading-[0.95] mb-6" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-accent);">
        About.
      </h1>
      <p class="reveal text-[var(--color-muted)] leading-relaxed max-w-[640px] text-lg">
        Final-year CS student at PES University. First-generation researcher. Building toward a research residency, MTech, and eventually an AGI-focused company — self-funded, deliberately.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <div class="container-prose"><div class="h-px bg-gradient-to-r from-transparent via-[var(--color-accent)]/20 to-transparent"></div></div>

  <!-- Bio -->
  <section class="container-prose pt-16 pb-10">
    <div class="reveal mb-6"><h2 class="section-heading">Bio</h2></div>

    <div class="narrative reveal">
      <p>
        I am a final-year B.Tech Computer Science student at <strong>PES University, Bengaluru</strong>, and a first-generation researcher. I am currently interning at <strong>Nagravision Kudelski</strong>, building agentic AI systems that orchestrate across enterprise knowledge bases, data lakes, and communication platforms.
      </p>
      <p>
        Where I am going: a research lab residency or MTech, then founding an AGI-focused company. Self-funded, deliberately. I believe the most meaningful work comes from taking the long path — building deep technical foundations before trying to scale, and keeping the independence to pursue questions that matter even when they are not fashionable.
      </p>
      <p class="text-[var(--color-muted)]">
        I am honest about being early. I do not yet have published papers or a PhD. What I do have is curiosity that does not quit, taste for the right problems, and a willingness to spend years on questions that matter. I would rather build real understanding slowly than collect credentials quickly.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Research Interests — long-form -->
  <section class="container-prose pb-10">
    <div class="reveal mb-6"><h2 class="section-heading">Research interests</h2></div>

    <div class="reveal grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 stagger">
      <div class="card p-5 shimmer-border">
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] font-bold">Core</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-2" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-accent);">Mechanistic Interpretability</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">Reverse-engineering what neural networks actually compute. The algorithms learned during training, not just the input/output map.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-5 shimmer-border">
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] font-bold">Structural</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-2" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-accent);">Architecture inductive biases</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">Attention, state-space, recurrent, convolutional. What each architecture makes easy vs. impossible to learn.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-5 shimmer-border">
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] font-bold">Scaling</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-2" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-accent);">Scaling laws & compute tradeoffs</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">How compute, data, and parameters trade off, and what that means for choosing between architecture families at a given budget.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-5 shimmer-border">
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] font-bold">Fine-tuning</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-2" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-accent);">LoRA · QLoRA · Quantization</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">MXFP4, GPTQ, AWQ. Effects on model behavior beyond just parameter efficiency — where the numerics bend what the model can do.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-5 shimmer-border">
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] font-bold">Central thread</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-2" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-accent);">Mesa-optimization</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">Models that learn to optimize <em>internally</em> during forward passes. Emergent optimization loops that aren't explicitly trained for — the subject of <a href="/projects/orpheus" class="ink-link">Orpheus</a>.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card p-5 shimmer-border">
        <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.14em] text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] font-bold">Applied</span>
        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold mt-2" style="font-family: var(--font-serif); color: var(--color-accent);">Mathematical reasoning</h3>
        <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">Pushing LLMs to solve competition-level mathematics through tool integration and structured reasoning. See <a href="/projects/ramanujan" class="ink-link">Ramanujan</a>.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Education -->
  <section class="container-prose pb-10">
    <div class="reveal mb-6"><h2 class="section-heading">Education</h2></div>

    <div class="stagger space-y-5">
      <div class="reveal flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-[#0F2A4A] to-[#1E4E7A] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">PES</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">PES University, Bengaluru</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">B.Tech, Computer Science and Engineering</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-1">
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-faint)]">2022 → 2026</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-faint)]">·</span>
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)]">CGPA 8.05 / 10</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-[#1E4E7A] to-[#4A90D9] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">PU</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">Sadhana PU College</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Pre-University (12th) · PCMC</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-1">
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)]">94.4%</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal flex gap-4">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-md bg-gradient-to-br from-[#4A90D9] to-[#7AB8F5] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">10</div>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">SRKVS</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">SSLC (10th)</p>
          <div class="flex items-center gap-3 mt-1">
            <span class="text-xs font-medium text-[var(--color-accent)]">99.4%</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-faint)]">·</span>
            <span class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)]">5th rank in state</span>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Experience -->
  <section class="container-prose pb-10">
    <div class="reveal mb-6"><h2 class="section-heading">Experience</h2></div>

    <div class="stagger space-y-5">
      <div class="reveal card overflow-hidden shimmer-border">
        <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#0F2A4A] to-[#4A90D9]"></div>
        <div class="p-5 md:p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-1 flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">Nagravision Kudelski</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Intern — Agentic AI Systems</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-faint)] whitespace-nowrap">Jan — May 2026</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Building Project Rick — an agentic chatbot that orchestrates across AWS Bedrock, Knowledge Bases, S3, Athena, Glue, and MS Teams. Designing the agent architecture, tool routing, and retrieval pipelines for enterprise knowledge access.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal card overflow-hidden shimmer-border">
        <div class="h-2 bg-gradient-to-r from-[#1E4E7A] to-[#7AB8F5]"></div>
        <div class="p-5 md:p-6">
          <div class="flex items-start justify-between mb-1 flex-wrap gap-2">
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">August AI</h3>
              <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)]">Intern — Machine Learning</p>
            </div>
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-faint)] whitespace-nowrap">Jun — Aug 2025</span>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-2 leading-relaxed">
            Worked on ML systems for Tata 1mg (grace platform) and Manipal Group. Applied machine learning to healthcare and enterprise use cases.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Competitions -->
  <section class="container-prose pb-10">
    <div class="reveal mb-6"><h2 class="section-heading">Competitions</h2></div>

    <div class="stagger grid gap-3">
      <div class="reveal flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-gold-soft)]/50 border border-[var(--color-gold)]/20">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">AI</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">
            AIMO Prize 3
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-gold-deep)] ml-2">36/50</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-0.5">Solo entry, 3 weeks of work. Kaggle competition for AI mathematical-olympiad solving. <a href="/projects/ramanujan" class="ink-link">Case study →</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-[var(--color-accent-soft)]/60 border border-[var(--color-accent)]/10">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-md bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">HV</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">
            Hackverse 2025, MIT Bangalore
            <span class="text-xs font-mono text-[var(--color-accent)] ml-2">7th place</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-0.5">Built WaySafe — a smart tourism-safety application. September 2025.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="reveal flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-lg bg-emerald-50/60 border border-emerald-200">
        <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-md bg-emerald-700 text-white text-xs font-bold flex items-center justify-center flex-shrink-0 mt-0.5">AR</div>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-[var(--color-ink)]" style="font-family: var(--font-serif);">
            ARC AGI 3
            <span class="pill pill-green ml-2">Active</span>
          </h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-0.5">Currently competing on Kaggle. Abstract reasoning and generalization benchmark.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Contact -->
  <section class="container-prose pb-20">
    <div class="reveal mb-6"><h2 class="section-heading">Contact</h2></div>

    <div class="reveal-scale card p-6 md:p-8">
      <p class="text-sm text-[var(--color-muted)] mb-4 leading-relaxed">
        Interested in collaborating on research, discussing AI systems, or just want to say hello? I am always happy to connect.
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 text-sm">
        <a href="mailto:aryanharitsa@gmail.com" class="btn-primary magnetic !text-xs">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"/></svg>
          aryanharitsa@gmail.com
        </a>
        <a href="https://github.com/Aryanharitsa" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-ghost magnetic !text-xs">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M12 0C5.37 0 0 5.37 0 12c0 5.31 3.435 9.795 8.205 11.385.6.105.825-.255.825-.57 0-.285-.015-1.23-.015-2.235-3.015.555-3.795-.735-4.035-1.41-.135-.345-.72-1.41-1.23-1.695-.42-.225-1.02-.78-.015-.795.945-.015 1.62.87 1.845 1.23 1.08 1.815 2.805 1.305 3.495.99.105-.78.42-1.305.765-1.605-2.67-.3-5.46-1.335-5.46-5.925 0-1.305.465-2.385 1.23-3.225-.12-.3-.54-1.53.12-3.18 0 0 1.005-.315 3.3 1.23.96-.27 1.98-.405 3-.405s2.04.135 3 .405c2.295-1.56 3.3-1.23 3.3-1.23.66 1.65.24 2.88.12 3.18.765.84 1.23 1.905 1.23 3.225 0 4.605-2.805 5.625-5.475 5.925.435.375.81 1.095.81 2.22 0 1.605-.015 2.895-.015 3.3 0 .315.225.69.825.57A12.02 12.02 0 0024 12c0-6.63-5.37-12-12-12z"/></svg>
          GitHub
        </a>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/aryan-haritsa-60292925b" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-ghost magnetic !text-xs">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path d="M20.447 20.452h-3.554v-5.569c0-1.328-.027-3.037-1.852-3.037-1.853 0-2.136 1.445-2.136 2.939v5.667H9.351V9h3.414v1.561h.046c.477-.9 1.637-1.85 3.37-1.85 3.601 0 4.267 2.37 4.267 5.455v6.286zM5.337 7.433a2.062 2.062 0 01-2.063-2.065 2.064 2.064 0 112.063 2.065zm1.782 13.019H3.555V9h3.564v11.452zM22.225 0H1.771C.792 0 0 .774 0 1.729v20.542C0 23.227.792 24 1.771 24h20.451C23.2 24 24 23.227 24 22.271V1.729C24 .774 23.2 0 22.222 0h.003z"/></svg>
          LinkedIn
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</Base>
